OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FFormer ITN correspondent Paul Davies
OL,8,Frecounts how he reported on the
OL,9,FRomanian Revolution of 1989, in what
OL,10,Fbecame Europe's bloodiest anti-
OL,11,Fcommunist uprising
OL,13,FDramatic unaired footage from the
OL,14,Ffrontline of the Romanian revolution
OL,15,Fin 1989 has been broadcast for the
OL,16,Ffirst time by ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
