OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FThe filming shows former ITN
OL,8,FCorrespondent Paul Davies and his
OL,9,Fcamera operator hiding between gunmen
OL,10,Fwho are trading shots during deadly
OL,11,Fstreet battles in Bucharest.
OL,13,FMore than 1,000 people were killed in
OL,14,Fwhat became Europe's bloodiest anti-
OL,15,Fcommunist uprising and would
OL,16,Fultimately topple Communist president
OL,17,FNicolae Ceausescu.
OL,26,@yD@M{y
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
