CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FThe previously unseen footage from the
OL,8,FChristmas-time conflict was played to
OL,9,FDavies in a new episode of Reporting
OL,10,FHistory, in which journalists join ITV
OL,11,FNews' Tom Bradby to revisit the most
OL,12,Fdramatic filming days from their
OL,13,Freporting careers.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
