CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FDavies was the only broadcaster to
OL,8,Freport from a besieged television
OL,9,Fstation that had become a key
OL,10,Fbattleground in the final days of the
OL,11,Fconflict after it had been taken over
OL,12,Fby revolutionaries who used it to
OL,13,Fbroadcast anti-Ceausescu messages.
OL,15,F"I was at the very centre of the
OL,16,Fbiggest story in the world at that
OL,17,Fmoment," Davies recounted. "Nobody
OL,18,Felse could get to (it) because it was
OL,19,Ftoo dangerous."
OL,26,@uD@T{yzD@SpmzD@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FIn the episode, the pair revisit a
OL,8,Ftelevised report from 1989 in which
OL,9,FDavies is seen reporting: "There was
OL,10,Fanother loud explosion here inside the
OL,11,FTV station - we are coming under
OL,12,Fattacks by bazookas at the moment."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,26,@tD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FDavies revealed to Bradby how close
OL,8,Fthose trapped in the threatened
OL,9,Fstation - including journalists who
OL,10,Fhad chosen not to flee - came to death
OL,11,Famid rumours Ceausescu's notorious
OL,12,Fsecret police were heading for it via
OL,13,Fsecret tunnels.
OL,15,F"Do they stay? Do they go? (The) safe
OL,16,Fthing is to go, because if the secret
OL,17,Fpolice do recapture it, nobody's
OL,18,Fcoming out alive," Davies said.
OL,26,@sD@R{ywD@\pmwD@`pn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,F"During that first period of five, six
OL,8,Fhours that we were there, there were
OL,9,Fstrong, strong rumours that the secret
OL,10,Fpolice had taken the building already."
OL,12,FDavies recounted making it through an
OL,13,F"incredibly frightening" first night
OL,14,Fin the TV station and filming it all,
OL,15,Fbefore making what he now regards as
OL,16,Fone of the "biggest mistakes" of his
OL,17,Fcareer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FIn order to broadcast the historic
OL,8,Ffootage to the world, he and his
OL,9,Fcamera operator needed to leave the
OL,10,Fbuilding to access their editing
OL,11,Fequipment which was "some distance"
OL,12,Faway.
OL,14,F"But then we had to get back to the TV
OL,15,Fstation to feed it," Davies continued.
OL,17,F"And that's the bit which I say was
OL,18,Fsuch a huge mistake. Because as we
OL,19,Farrived back, the second wave of the
OL,20,Fattack started."
OL,26,@sD@UOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FDavies described how he was smuggled
OL,8,Finto the TV station in the back of a
OL,9,Fmakeshift ambulance that was
OL,10,Fsurrounded by gunfire.
OL,12,F"We were told to lie on the floor of
OL,13,Fit and it drove us across the square
OL,14,Fbetween the two sides that were
OL,15,Fshooting each other," Davies said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,F"It was a horrible journey because in
OL,8,Fthe car, and particularly the floor
OL,9,Fwhere we were lying, was pools of
OL,10,Fblood and unmentionable things in it
OL,11,Ffrom the job (the ambulance) had been
OL,12,Fdoing overnight."
OL,14,FHis crew then had to lie under an
OL,15,Farmoured vehicle for almost two hours,
OL,16,Fwhile bullets hit nearby objects.
OL,18,FReflecting on that moment, he said he
OL,19,Fvowed to "never leave the (TV station)
OL,20,Fagain, if there was any choice".
OL,26,@sD@NpmsD@\pn{D@[pm{D@fpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
