CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775851553
OL,3,CWar reporter shown unaired footage of
OL,4,Chim under fire in 1989 Romanian
OL,5,Cuprising
OL,7,FCommunist dictator Ceausescu's brutal
OL,8,F24-year rule had been defined by
OL,9,Fsuppressing civil liberties, leaving
OL,10,Fmuch of the country in poverty.
OL,12,FHe was overthrown in the final days of
OL,13,F1989 after another typically violent
OL,14,Fcrackdown of protestors saw hundreds
OL,15,Fof thousands take to the streets of
OL,16,Fthe Romanian capital Bucharest.
OL,18,FThe uprising ultimately saw Ceausescu
OL,19,Fand his wife Elena shot dead by firing
OL,20,Fsquad on Christmas Day.
OL,26,@oD@X{yzD@a{y
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
